    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃーん！　深夜に失礼しまーす！\nラーメン愛から、小美山愛が出前のお届けでーす！",
      "startTime": 6.3999999046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.1666669051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は優ちゃんのおた～んじょ～び～～！\nという訳でご用意したのは～～……こちら！",
      "startTime": 15.8999999046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3666665713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "『愛の愛情たっぷり特選バースデーラーメン\n～優ちゃんエディション～』でございます！",
      "startTime": 22.5666665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.9666679223
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.2666665713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "最高級食材をふんだんに使用！　味には自信ありです！\nちなみに推定1800キロカロリーとなっております！",
      "startTime": 29.2666665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.233334589
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.3666665713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうな。でも、深夜にハイカロリーはご法度……\nまあええか。だって今日はうち、誕生日やし？",
      "startTime": 39.5666665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.6666679223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "私も一緒に食べるし平気です！\nそれじゃあチュルチュルッといきましょう！\nハッピーバースデー！　優ちゃん！",
      "startTime": 50.2333332379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.2333332379
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.133334589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "せーの\nいただきまーす！",
      "startTime": 54.4333332379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.4666709741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "はふ、はふはふ……\nなんやこれ美味し、語彙が吹き飛ぶ……！",
      "startTime": 61.7000029564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.3333376408
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.9999999046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、こんなんあかんのに、箸が止まらへん！\n愛ちゃん！　替え玉ちょうだ～～～～～い！！",
      "startTime": 71.3000029564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.7666696231
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "あ～美味しかった……！　これぞ深夜の背徳感！\nどうでしたか、優ちゃん？",
      "startTime": 83.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.9666719914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ごちそうさま、大変美味しゅうございました……\nあ、それでこれ、カロリーが、なんぼやったっけ……",
      "startTime": 91.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.9666719914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "推定1800キロカロリーとなっております\nあ、替え玉追加したから2000は超えたかも？",
      "startTime": 99.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.4333386581
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あかんわ、これどないしよ……\n明日から一週間は断食せな……",
      "startTime": 106.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.8000073593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "え～、大丈夫ですよ～。だって誕生日はいくら食べても\nゼロカロリーってこころが言ってましたもん！",
      "startTime": 114.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.7666740259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃん、また愛ちゃんをおちょくって……\nてか、その理論なら愛ちゃんはゼロにはならへんで！？",
      "startTime": 121.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13166.666666599995,
          "startTime": 135.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.1000032903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、私は1800キロカロリーでぶん殴られちゃう！\nこうなったら……！　優ちゃん、ついて来て下さい！",
      "startTime": 131.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-001-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_noon",
      "startTime": 137.2166648707
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "いっちに、いっちに……！\n食べた分は～……使えばいい！",
      "startTime": 140.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、これめっちゃキツいわ……！\nこれやったら2000なんかすぐやな……！",
      "startTime": 147.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3399.998204100001,
          "startTime": 150.4333315374
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　1セットで20キロカロリーの消費だから……\n100セット繰り返せば2000キロなんてすぐです！",
      "startTime": 154.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "どこがすぐやねん！　理不尽や～～～～～！\n全然釣り合い取れてへんやんか～～～～～！",
      "startTime": 161.6999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "食べたら動く！　動けば燃える！\n明日の優ちゃんを作るのは、今日の食事と運動です！",
      "startTime": 167.6666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "『愛の愛情たっぷり特選バースデー筋トレ\n～優ちゃんエディション～』で理想の体を作ろう！",
      "startTime": 175.1666656494,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3966.670974200014,
          "startTime": 179.1333366236
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "さあ優ちゃんご一緒に！\nう～～～……シックスパ～～～～～ック！！",
      "startTime": 181.6333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "し、シックスパ～～～ック……！！",
      "startTime": 185.8000032903,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}